# Parking Management System Project Structure

## 1. Start.java

Purpose:

* Main starting point of the application
* Runs the ParkingGUI using SwingUtilities

Contains:

* main() method
* GUI launch logic

---

## 2. entity/Vehicle.java

Purpose:

* Vehicle entity/model class
* Stores all vehicle information

Contains:

* Private variables:

  * vehicleId
  * driverName
  * vehicleType
  * numberPlate
  * parkingSlot
  * entryTime

Methods:

* Constructor
* Getter methods
* Setter methods
* toLine()

  * Converts object into CSV format
* fromLine()

  * Converts CSV text into Vehicle object
* toRow()

  * Converts Vehicle object into JTable row array

---

## 3. fileio/VehicleFileIO.java

Purpose:

* Handles all File I/O operations
* Database management using text file

Contains:

* FILE_NAME path
* TEMP_FILE path

Methods:

1. createFileIfNotExists()

* Creates database file if not available

2. countRecords()

* Counts total vehicle records

3. generateVehicleId()

* Generates automatic serial Vehicle ID

4. generateParkingSlot()

* Automatically assigns available parking slot

5. addVehicle()

* Adds vehicle into text database

6. getAllVehicles()

* Bulk retrieval of all vehicle data

7. searchVehicles()

* Searches vehicle by:

  * Vehicle ID
  * Driver Name
  * Number Plate

8. getVehicleById()

* Retrieves a single vehicle using ID

9. deleteVehicle()

* Deletes vehicle from database using temporary file

CRUD Operations:

* Create ✅
* Read ✅
* Delete ✅

---

## 4. gui/ParkingGUI.java

Purpose:

* Main Java Swing GUI interface

Contains:

GUI Components:

* JFrame
* JPanel
* JTable
* JScrollPane
* JTextField
* JComboBox
* JButton
* JLabel

GUI Sections:

1. Title Panel
2. Search Panel
3. Button Panel
4. Vehicle Information Form
5. JTable Vehicle List

Features:

* Vehicle Entry
* Vehicle Exit
* Search Vehicle
* View All
* Clear Fields

Parking Features:

* Auto parking slot generation
* Automatic date-time save
* Parking charge calculation
* Bike entry fee = 30 TK
* Car entry fee = 40 TK
* Hourly parking fee = 10 TK

Extra Features:

* JTable row selection
* Centered application window
* Professional GUI layout
* Modern white theme

Helper Methods:

* createBlueButton()
* createWhiteButton()
* createLabel()
* createTextField()
* styleCombo()

Functional Methods:

* addVehicle()
* exitVehicle()
* searchVehicle()
* viewAll()
* clearFields()

---

## 5. fileio/vehicles.txt

Purpose:

* Text file database

Stores:

* Vehicle ID
* Driver Name
* Vehicle Type
* Number Plate
* Parking Slot
* Entry Time

Example:
V-00001,Forhad,Bike,DHAKA-GHA-1234,A-1,16-05-2026 11:50 PM

---

## 6. fileio/temp.txt

Purpose:

* Temporary file used during delete operation

Used for:

* Safe file handling
* Preventing data corruption
